Turn off the internet connection to observer the behaviour of the HTML Page 

and Turn it on again: (Without reloading the page). Network status has been handled

in this piece of contact form. While filling the form if the internet is turned off

the user get notified by a big red coloured toolbar saying OFFLINE. More appealing 

and user friendly when he gets the message as OFFLINE (red colored) or ONLINE (green colored).

Consists of other HTML5 festures and special tags.
